<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> tiṅkaḷum voli Aḻinta <unclear>ci</unclear>ntūramuñ ceṅkai nallāc caṅkamum
<lb n="2"/>koṅkaip puḷakamun tāṅkit tavaṉa <unclear>virap</unclear>poraṅkulil veṉṟaruḷuṅ kālakālaṉ ka 
